❗NEW PRODUCT❗
This Friday our Bee Cute short overalls presale drops!
We are still new to clothing and are using presales to fund manufacturing 🐝🍯 
Good news, the manufacturing time isn't so long 😉🤞
Thank you to everyone who supports our clothing range, we have two more pieces coming this Friday also!
.
Everything is in place to go ahead with Fridays drop, we are still recovering from covid but hoping to be feeling better by next week 🤞🤞
Please understand there are delays in pin club post and email replies due to this.
.
.
.

node.text:
Meet Soy!
The non-profit charity plush 🐧
(Link in bio)
Full story:
My recently turned 6yo daughter had her first experience with the real world when she found out her favourite birds are endangered.
Then she learnt that she can help.
After the initial "mummy give all your money to the penguins now! Quickly!"
She decided to create Soy with the intention to (with my help) make her into a plush toy to sell to raise money for charity. Soy, a cute baby emperor penguin, who loves her parents so much, she wears a hat that looks like them.
The plush she designed will be crowdfunded for manufacturing costs and have all profits donated to @wwf @wwf_uk to help save the penguins and contribute towards climate crisis.
.
Her Kickstarter link is in my bio
.
.
.
#plushiecommunity #plushiesoninstagram #plushtoy #plushielife #plush #plushcollector #plushiefriends #plushtoys #homeeducation #homeschooling #savethepenguins #emperorpenguin #emperorpenguins #emperorpenguinchick #charitywork #charityproject #wwf #worldwildlifefund #worldwildlifefoundation #charitysale #nonprofit
